data.description: Welcome to this charming older home in Up Town Oakridge steps from the distillery, brew pub, coffee shops, and more. Located on a corner, large dividable lot, this home features new laminate flooring, newer vinyl windows, a step in shower in the master bath, but retains the charm of yesteryear with 9' ceilings, a clawfoot tub in the main bath, large kitchen with wooden countertops, and an indoor laundry with utility sink. Fully fenced with room to garden this is a wonderful place to call home!
